Label: NAMA PROVINSI
label_english: Province name

Label: NAMA KABUPATEN/KOTA
label_english: Regency/city name

Label: NAMA KECAMATAN
label_english: Sub -district name

Label: NAMA DESA/KELURAHAN
label_english: Village/kelurahan name

Label: STATUS DEFINITIF DESA DAN OPERASIONAL DESA/KELURAHAN: ADA WILAYAH DESA/KELURAHAN DENGAN BATAS YANG JELAS
label_english: Village Definitive Status and Village/Kelurahan Operations: There is a village/kelurahan area with a clear boundary
Aggregation Method: proportion of villages in the regency with a clear boundary
Notes: For calculating the village level proportions at the regency level, your denominator needs to be the total number of villages in the regency, and the nominator needs to be the number of villages in the regency with a given characteristic

Label: STATUS DEFINITIF DESA DAN OPERASIONAL DESA/KELURAHAN: ADA PENDUDUK YANG MENETAP DI WILAYAH DESA/KELURAHAN
label_english: Village Definitive Status and Village/Kelurahan Operations: There are residents who settled in the village/kelurahan area
Aggregation Method: proportion of villages in the regency with residents who settled in the village/kelurahan area

Label: STATUS DEFINITIF DESA DAN OPERASIONAL DESA/KELURAHAN: ADA PEMERINTAH DESA/KELURAHAN
label_english: Village Definitive Status and Village/Kelurahan Operations: There is a Village/Kelurahan Government
Aggregation Method: proportion of villages in the regency with residents who settled in the village/kelurahan area

Label: STATUS PEMERINTAHAN
label_english: Government status
Aggregation Method: This needs to be broken down into a separate category for each government status (you can create dummy variables for each). Then use proportion (i.e. Proportion of villages with government status == desa, proportion of villages with govt status == Kelurahan, etc.)

Label: BADAN PERMUSYAWARATAN DESA/LEMBAGA MUSYAWARAH KELURAHAN
label_english: Village Consultative Body/Village Deliberation Institution
Aggregation Method: Create dummies for each option: "ada"/"tidak ada". Then calculate proportion (i.e. proportion of villages in the regency with and without consultative body)

Label: JUMLAH KEGIATAN MUSYAWARAH DESA/KELURAHAN YANG DILAKUKAN SELAMA TAHUN 2019
label_english: The number of village/kelurahan deliberations carried out during 2019
Aggregation Method: average number of discussions per village in the regency

Label: PETA DESA/KELURAHAN YANG DITETAPKAN DALAM PERATURAN BUPATI/WALIKOTA ATAU GUBERNUR
label_english: Map of the village/kelurahan stipulated in the Regent/Mayor Regulation or Governor
Aggregation Method: Create dummies for each option: "ada"/"tidak ada". Then calculate proportion

Label: JUMLAH KELUARGA PENGGUNA LISTRIK PLN
label_english: Number of families of PLN electricity users
Aggregation Method: proportion of families in the regency with PLN electricity
Notes: here, you may want to create a new variable with the total number of families in each village using this information, which will be helpful to calculate the hosuehold level proportions

Label: JUMLAH KELUARGA PENGGUNA LISTRIK NON PLN
label_english: Number of Non PLN Electric User Families
Aggregation Method: proportion of families in the regency with non-PLN electricity

Label: JUMLAH KELUARGA BUKAN PENGGUNA LISTRIK
label_english: Number of Families Non -Electric User
Aggregation Method: proportion of families in the recency with no-electricity

Label: PENERANGAN DI JALAN UTAMA DESA/KELURAHAN
label_english: Lighting on the main road/kelurahan road
Aggregation Method: create dummy variables for each option (yes, most of them; yes, some of them; yes there isn't) then calculate the proportion of villages in the regency for each of the options

Label: JIKA ADA PENERANGAN DI JALAN UTAMA DESA/KELURAHAN (R402A BERKODE 1 ATAU 2), JENIS PENERANGAN
label_english: If there is lighting on the main road of the village/kelurahan (R402A coded 1 or 2), the type of lighting
Aggregation Method: create dummy variables for each type of lighting (i.e. provided by govt. / provided by NGOs / "non-electric") and then calculate the proportion of villages in the regency with each type of lighting

Label: BAHAN BAKAR UNTUK MEMASAK YANG DIGUNAKAN OLEH KELUARGA: GAS KOTA
label_english: Fuel for cooking used by families: city gas
Aggregation Method: proportion of families in the regency that use city gas for cooking fuel
Notes: For calculating the proportions of household level variables at the regency level, your denominator has to be the total number of households in the regency. The nominator needs to be the total number of households in the regency that has a given characteristic. In order to do this, you wil first want to create a variable that has the total number of families in each village.

Label: BAHAN BAKAR UNTUK MEMASAK YANG DIGUNAKAN OLEH KELUARGA: LPG 3 KG
label_english: Fuel for cooking used by family: LPG 3 kg
Aggregation Method: proportion of families in the regency  that use LPG for cooking fuel

Label: BAHAN BAKAR UNTUK MEMASAK YANG DIGUNAKAN OLEH KELUARGA: LPG LEBIH DARI 3 KG
label_english: Fuel for cooking used by the family: LPG is more than 3 kg
Aggregation Method: proportion of families  in the regency that use LPG >3KG for cooking fuel

Label: BAHAN BAKAR UNTUK MEMASAK YANG DIGUNAKAN OLEH KELUARGA: MINYAK TANAH
label_english: Fuel for cooking used by the family: kerosene
Aggregation Method: proportion of families  in the regency that use kerosene for cooking fuel

Label: BAHAN BAKAR UNTUK MEMASAK YANG DIGUNAKAN OLEH KELUARGA: KAYU BAKAR
label_english: Fuel for cooking used by the family: firewood
Aggregation Method: proportion of families in the regency  that use firewood for cooking fuel

Label: BAHAN BAKAR UNTUK MEMASAK YANG DIGUNAKAN OLEH KELUARGA: LAINNYA
label_english: Fuel for cooking used by the family: Others
Aggregation Method: proportion of families  in the regency  that use others for cooking fuel

Label: BAHAN BAKAR UNTUK MEMASAK SEBAGIAN BESAR KELUARGA:
label_english: Fuel for cooking most families:
Aggregation Method: create dummy variables for each option (1-6) and calculate the proportion families  in the regency that use each option the most frequently

Label: TEMPAT BUANG SAMPAH KELUARGA: TEMPAT SAMPAH, KEMUDIAN DIANGKUT

Label: TEMPAT BUANG SAMPAH KELUARGA: DALAM LUBANG ATAU DIBAKAR

Label: TEMPAT BUANG SAMPAH KELUARGA: DRAINASE (GOT/SELOKAN)

Label: TEMPAT BUANG SAMPAH KELUARGA: LAINNYA
label_english: Family Trash Place: Others
Aggregation Method: proportion of families  in the regency  that use xx for garbage disposal

Label: TEMPAT BUANG SAMPAH SEBAGIAN BESAR KELUARGA
label_english: Place to throw garbage most of the families
